import React from 'react' export const currency = props => { const { name, symbol, price_usd, percent_change_1h, percent_change_24h, percent_change_7d, } = props.data return (

  • {name} ({symbol})

    ${(+price_usd).toFixed(2)}

    {percent_change_1h}% 1hr

    {percent_change_24h}% 24hrs

    {percent_change_7d}% 7days

    • ) }
